{
  "id": "onDuQF5e",
  "slug": "stylish-effects",
  "title": "Stylish Effects",
  "description": "Status effect display overhaul: Display them in any menu! And way more compact.",
  "body": "<p><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/fmWwWkZ.png\" width=\"854\" height=\"240\" /></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/askYVd2.png\" width=\"854\" height=\"14\" /></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center; line-height: 36px;\"><img src=\"https://img.shields.io/badge/Available%20for%20Minecraft-1.19%20%7C%201.18%20%7C%201.17%20%7C%201.16-ecebe6?labelColor=2F4858&amp;style=for-the-badge\" width=\"386\" height=\"28\" />&emsp;<img src=\"https://img.shields.io/badge/Install%20on-Client%20Only-ecebe6?labelColor=2F4858&amp;style=for-the-badge\" width=\"210\" height=\"28\" /></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center; line-height: 36px;\"><a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/stylish-effects/files/all?filter-status=1&amp;filter-game-version=2020709689%3A7498\"><img src=\"https://bit.ly/3yrSsw7\" width=\"320\" height=\"28\" /></a>&emsp;<a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/puzzles-lib\"><img src=\"https://bit.ly/3jr9xQw\" width=\"215\" height=\"28\" /></a></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center; line-height: 36px;\"><a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/stylish-effects/files/all?filter-status=1&amp;filter-game-version=2020709689%3A7499\"><img src=\"https://bit.ly/3nRXr4m\" width=\"325\" height=\"28\" /></a>&emsp;<a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/fabric-api\"><img src=\"https://bit.ly/30lZmFY\" width=\"208\" height=\"28\" /></a>&emsp;<a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/puzzles-lib\"><img src=\"https://bit.ly/3jr9xQw\" width=\"215\" height=\"28\" /></a>&emsp;<a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/forge-config-api-port-fabric\"><img src=\"https://bit.ly/3clkhvn\" width=\"299\" height=\"28\" /></a></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/askYVd2.png\" width=\"854\" height=\"14\" /></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 20px;\"><strong>📖 About:</strong></span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><strong>Stylish Effects</strong> completely overhauls how status effects are displayed. There are multiple modes to choose and countless configuration options available to create the effects display of your dreams.</span></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/askYVd2.png\" width=\"854\" height=\"14\" /></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 20px;\"><strong>📚 Contents:</strong></span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">First of all, the crummy little vanilla hud effects display is replaced with a fancier version which includes an effect timer as well as the current effect amplifier. This display is also now used in the inventory, as it's way more compact and allows for many more effects to be shown before they start to overlap. And this new inventory display is no longer limited to the player inventory, now you can see your active effects in every container!</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">But wait, now that status effects are shown small and compact with just an icon, how will you find out how your active effects are called? Don't worry, a handy tooltip is added for that. The tooltip will be even more useful when <span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/just-enough-effect-descriptions-jeed\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><strong>Just Enough Effect Descriptions</strong></span></a> by <span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/members/mehvahdjukaar\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><strong>MehVahdJukaar</strong></span></a> is installed.</span></span></span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">You like the vanilla inventory status effect display and want to keep it or even use it on the hud as well? No problem! You can choose any widget mode you want, or even none. Alongside that there are many configurable settings, such as the screen side for effects, amount of rows and columns, a custom alpha value, text colors, custom screen positions, and much, much more.</span></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/askYVd2.png\" width=\"854\" height=\"14\" /></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 20px;\"><strong>📷 Media:</strong></span></p>\n<table style=\"text-align: center;\">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td><img src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/480/288/2022-07-23_22.png\" width=\"410\" height=\"231\" /></td>\n<td>&emsp;&emsp;</td>\n<td><img src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/480/290/2022-07-23_22.png\" width=\"410\" height=\"231\" /></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><strong>Stylish effects in action being very stylish</strong></td>\n<td>&emsp;&emsp;</td>\n<td><strong>Various effect render types can be chosen and configured</strong></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>&nbsp;</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><img src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/480/291/2022-07-23_22.png\" width=\"410\" height=\"231\" /></td>\n<td>&emsp;&emsp;</td>\n<td><img src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/480/292/2022-07-23_22.png\" width=\"410\" height=\"231\" /></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><strong>Compact effects replace the vanilla display inside of the inventory</strong></td>\n<td>&emsp;&emsp;</td>\n<td><strong>The effects display is shown in every container, not just the inventory</strong></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>&nbsp;</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><img src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/480/293/2022-07-23_22.png\" width=\"410\" height=\"231\" /></td>\n<td>&emsp;&emsp;</td>\n<td><img src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/480/294/2022-07-23_22.png\" width=\"410\" height=\"231\" /></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><strong>Useful tooltips will appear when effect widgets are hovered</strong></td>\n<td>&emsp;&emsp;</td>\n<td><strong>So many possible settings, create your very own effect display</strong></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>&nbsp;</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><img src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/480/295/2022-07-23_22.png\" width=\"410\" height=\"231\" /></td>\n<td>&emsp;&emsp;</td>\n<td>&nbsp;</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><strong>Great JEI and REI compatibility</strong></td>\n<td>&emsp;&emsp;</td>\n<td>&nbsp;</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>&nbsp;</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<p><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/askYVd2.png\" width=\"854\" height=\"14\" /></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 20px;\"><strong>💡 FAQ:</strong></span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><strong>Q: How do I configure this mod on Forge?</strong><br /><strong>A:</strong> Install my <span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/config-menus-forge\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><strong>Config Menus for Forge</strong></span></a> mod and do it directly in-game!</span></span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><strong>Q: How do I configure this mod on Fabric?</strong><br /><strong>A:</strong> Editing configs directly in-game has not yet been implemented. Instead when in a world run the <code>/config showfile &lt;modid&gt;</code> command by choosing either <code>CLIENT</code> or <code>SERVER</code> (depending on the mod), then click the file name (ending with .toml) that appears in chat to be able to manually edit the config file in a separate editor. After saving the file, the config will automatically reload in-game after a couple of seconds, so no game restart required.</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><strong>Q: Where can I download this mod for Fabric on versions of Minecraft before 1.19?</strong><br /><strong>A:</strong> Older downloads are found on the <a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/stylish-effects-fabric\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><strong>old project page</strong></span></a>.</span></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/askYVd2.png\" width=\"854\" height=\"14\" /></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 20px;\"><strong>🏆 Credits:</strong></span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">Developing Stylish Effects was helped and inspired by:</span></p>\n<ul>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/members/deadzoke\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><strong>Deadzoke</strong></span></a> for inspiring the effect timer display from their <a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/ignitehud\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">Ignite HUD</span></a> mod</span></li>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/members/dmitrylovin\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><strong>Dmitrylovin</strong></span></a> for inspiring the compact effect amplifier display from their <a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/inventory-hud-forge\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">Inventory HUD+</span></a> mod</span></li>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/members/snownee_\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><strong>Snownee</strong></span></a> for a small hack for disabling the default JEI inventory status effect handling from their <a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/mini-effects\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">Mini Effects</span></a> mod</span></li>\n</ul>\n<p><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/askYVd2.png\" width=\"854\" height=\"14\" /></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center; line-height: 36px;\"><a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/members/lunapixelstudios/projects\"><img src=\"https://img.shields.io/static/v1?label=CurseForge&amp;message=LunaPixelStudios&amp;color=ecebe6&amp;labelColor=2F4858&amp;style=for-the-badge&amp;logo=curseforge&amp;logoColor=white\" width=\"282\" height=\"28\" /></a>&emsp;<a href=\"https://twitter.com/LunaPixelStudio\"><img src=\"https://img.shields.io/twitter/follow/LunaPixelStudio?label=Twitter&amp;color=ecebe6&amp;labelColor=2F4858&amp;style=for-the-badge&amp;logo=twitter&amp;logoColor=white\" width=\"149\" height=\"28\" /></a>&emsp;<a href=\"https://discord.gg/8ZmhaPPbjE\"><img src=\"https://img.shields.io/discord/790272037578473512?label=Discord&amp;color=ecebe6&amp;labelColor=2F4858&amp;style=for-the-badge&amp;logo=discord&amp;logoColor=white\" width=\"220\" height=\"28\" /></a></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/1MOyd2u.png\" width=\"854\" height=\"300\" /></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center; line-height: 36px;\"><a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/members/fuzs_/projects\"><img src=\"https://img.shields.io/static/v1?label=&amp;message=Fuzs_&amp;color=ecebe6&amp;labelColor=2F4858&amp;style=for-the-badge&amp;logo=curseforge&amp;logoColor=white\" width=\"97\" height=\"28\" /></a>&emsp;<a href=\"https://github.com/Fuzss\"><img src=\"https://img.shields.io/static/v1?label=&amp;message=Fuzss&amp;color=ecebe6&amp;labelColor=2F4858&amp;style=for-the-badge&amp;logo=github&amp;logoColor=white\" width=\"97\" height=\"28\" /></a>&emsp;<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/channel/UC2l26SuCmCNSCPefpfbCX7Q\"><img src=\"https://img.shields.io/static/v1?label=&amp;message=Fuzs&amp;color=ecebe6&amp;labelColor=2F4858&amp;style=for-the-badge&amp;logo=youtube&amp;logoColor=white\" width=\"89\" height=\"28\" /></a>&emsp;<a href=\"https://twitter.com/Fusseel\"><img src=\"https://img.shields.io/static/v1?label=&amp;message=@Fusseel&amp;color=ecebe6&amp;labelColor=2F4858&amp;style=for-the-badge&amp;logo=twitter&amp;logoColor=white\" width=\"124\" height=\"28\" /></a>&emsp;<a href=\"https://www.reddit.com/user/Fusseel\"><img src=\"https://img.shields.io/static/v1?label=&amp;message=u/Fusseel&amp;color=ecebe6&amp;labelColor=2F4858&amp;style=for-the-badge&amp;logo=reddit&amp;logoColor=white\" alt=\"Reddit\" width=\"130\" height=\"28\" /></a>&emsp;<img src=\"https://img.shields.io/static/v1?label=&amp;message=Fuzs%200212&amp;color=ecebe6&amp;labelColor=2F4858&amp;style=for-the-badge&amp;logo=discord&amp;logoColor=white\" width=\"127\" height=\"28\" /></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/askYVd2.png\" width=\"854\" height=\"14\" /></p>\n<table style=\"text-align: center;\">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td><a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/config-menus-forge\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/kiHP8s9.png\" width=\"410\" height=\"115\" /></a></td>\n<td>&emsp;&emsp;</td>\n<td><a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/better-animations-collection\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/OVV5lXk.png\" width=\"410\" height=\"115\" /></a></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>&nbsp;</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/trading-post\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/UzgNFIB.png\" width=\"410\" height=\"115\" /></a></td>\n<td>&emsp;&emsp;</td>\n<td><a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/pick-up-notifier\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/DCwxKZU.png\" width=\"410\" height=\"115\" /></a></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>&nbsp;</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/console-experience\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/aXWOS7B.png\" width=\"410\" height=\"115\" /></a></td>\n<td>&emsp;&emsp;</td>\n<td><a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/easy-magic\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/Mlxi8cy.png\" width=\"410\" height=\"115\" /></a></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>&nbsp;</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/visual-workbench\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/DTzDrbm.png\" width=\"410\" height=\"115\" /></a></td>\n<td>&emsp;&emsp;</td>\n<td><a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/diagonal-fences\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/mU9OlhP.png\" width=\"410\" height=\"115\" /></a></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>&nbsp;</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/golden-age-combat\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/sHiR309.png\" width=\"410\" height=\"115\" /></a></td>\n<td>&emsp;&emsp;</td>\n<td><a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/air-hop\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/MinxlVJ.png\" width=\"410\" height=\"115\" /></a></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>&nbsp;</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<p><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/askYVd2.png\" width=\"854\" height=\"14\" /></p>",
